OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe evening
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy with scattered showers,
OL,7,Fsome heavy and thundery. These showers
OL,8,Fbecome isolated from late evening as
OL,9,Fthe odd clear spell develops.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FChance of a shower at first
OL,12,Facross Argyll, otherwise a dry morning
OL,13,Fwith some early brightness. Cloud in
OL,14,Fthe afternoon with occasional rain
OL,15,Fspreading north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
